  "title": "Test & Compliance Technician (Lighting / Electrical) #79907",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacture and Repair of Electrical Equipment</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Test & Compliance Technician (Lighting / Electrical)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Ang Mo Kio Ave 5</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday, 8AM-5:30PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT Pay + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in planning and conducting technical tests on lighting products, with a focus on emergency lighting performance and safety standards.</li><li>Prepare and maintain technical documentation and compliance files required for product certifications, including SS 563 and other relevant standards.</li><li>Collaborate with the engineering team to identify and resolve any non-compliance issues found during testing.</li><li>Maintain, calibrate, and operate laboratory equipment while ensuring a safe and well-organized testing environment.</li><li>Keep up to date with lighting standards, regulations, and industry developments, particularly in emergency lighting compliance.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>NITEC, Higher NITEC, or Diploma in Electrical Engineering or a related discipline.</li><li>Strong interest in product testing, compliance, and safety standards, especially in emergency lighting systems.</li><li>Familiarity with testing equipment, data collection, and analysis will be an advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79907 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
